---
title: Veggie Mince & Rosemary Pie with Cheesy Mash Top & Garlic Greens
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped number. It's just like Nanna used to make (but better!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-rosemary-cottage-pie-3012320d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/veggie-rosemary-cottage-pie-606e7c5e05cb79557254a048-a874e9f1.pdf
servings: 2
